<article class="row hentry post-270110 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-covid-19 tag-economy tag-election-2020 tag-elections-health tag-governors tag-politics section-politics-and-elections primary_topic-politics" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ReportageNewsArticle">
