<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/texas-lt-governor-says-seniors-should-risk-dying-of-covid-19-to-protect-economy/" title="Texas Lt. Governor Says Seniors Should Risk Dying of COVID-19 to Protect Economy">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-dan-patrick-coronavirus-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Lt. Gov. Dan Patrick speaks at the Republican Party of Texas State Convention at the Kay Bailey Hutchison Convention Center, May 12, 2016, in Dallas." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-dan-patrick-coronavirus-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-dan-patrick-coronavirus-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-dan-patrick-coronavirus-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-dan-patrick-coronavirus-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-dan-patrick-coronavirus-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/news/' rel='category' class='news'>News</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/environment-and-health/' rel='section' class='environment-and-health' style='color: #0ba864;'>Environment &amp; Health</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/texas-lt-governor-says-seniors-should-risk-dying-of-covid-19-to-protect-economy/">Texas Lt. Governor Says Seniors Should Risk Dying of COVID-19 to Protect Economy</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Texas lawmakers and other observers reacted with alarm to Lieutenant Gov. Dan Patrick&#8217;s remarks on Fox News.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
